Now the query is `icmp slt i32 %x, %y`, which is `%x < %y`, i.e., `%y - %x > 0`. 

We know `%z + %x < %y` and we also know `%z >= 0` (from range metadata). So `%x <= %z + %x < %y`, hence `%x < %y`.

